Name: Berserker Commando
Difficulty: medium
Connections: uses Doom 2 sounds
Summon: BerserkerCommando
Melee: yes
Distance: no
Type: Human, Undead
Brightmaps: yes
Actor modification: no
ACS: no

Description:
This former commando has been injected with an experimental Berserk serum.
Now he is twice as sturdy, very fast, extremely pain resistant and packs a deadly punch.
Can perform an attack combo, every 4th punch in a row is extra devastating. Keep your distance!